  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Wind through a hollow bone. High breath, low partials, filter resonance peaked to create the singing quality of air through a narrow tube. The formant shape gives it an almost vocal quality — not quite a voice, not quite a flute, but the ancestor of both. Played in low registers it becomes a didgeridoo drone.",
